			<DIV>Is there any chance of tuning the bard epic 1.5?&nbsp; To be quite blunt, the bard epic requires a crazy amount of raiding.&nbsp; In addition, two of the raids are one of the most distant zones in the game (Dragon Necropolis).&nbsp; We have no problem winning, but the amount of guild time required for each 1.5 is really high!</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Thanks!</DIV>
