			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV></DIV>Dont know why I couldnt remember where the post was..&nbsp; /boggle self<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
&nbsp;<SPAN> 
<DIV><BR><STRONG><FONT color=#ffff00>8. Concerns for the new epic 1.5&nbsp; </FONT></STRONG></DIV>
<DIV>Our epic 1.5 quest seems disproportionately difficult. The weapon, stat-wise, is fair but the damage/delay ratio is below PoTime weapons (while every other epic is above it) and it would be proper to balance this weapon to match the Beastlords 1.5. The instrument mod, even after the change seems low. Bards at this level can easily replace/exceed the instrument mod given an would welcome an effect not so easily lost.&nbsp; <STRONG><FONT color=#ff0000>The weapon is tuned and is on par with other weapons from Plane of Time.&nbsp; There are no plans at this time to modify this weapon.</FONT></STRONG></DIV></SPAN><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
